user.canProvide: Workshopping ideas, meeting new community members, chatting about product improvements.
user.intro: I'm the product ops manager at Contrary working to support all new and budding products launching at Contrary (but mostly Research). Love running, horror movies, and reading!
user.lookingFor: Meet more of the Contrary community.
user.meetWithBlurb: Happy to chat about product ops, early-stage startup life, and entering the startup ecosystem with a nontraditional background
